Invoking: `validate` with `{'patch': "--- a/ext/dom/document.c
+++ b/ext/dom/document.c
@@ -1727,6 +1727,22 @@ static int dom_perform_xinclude(xmlDocPtr docp, dom_object *intern, zend_long flags)

